rows.name:
In fiction, Lapupu can become anyone!
Like swishy-swashy hero or fluffy-puff
princess or zip-a-zip fairy!

rows.label: tlk4210018304_msg0002
rows.name:
But not able to touch world of fiction.
Not see or smell either.

rows.label: tlk4210018304_msg0003
rows.name:
When Lapupu a bit older, Lapupu want
to go on great adventure, see Alst!
Maybe then will find real-life fairy!
